pt.ua.dicoogle.sdk.utils

Class DICOMObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.ua.dicoogle.sdk.utils.DICOMObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MappedDICOMObject, MappedDICOMObjectDecorator

    public abstract class DICOMObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
    An interface that maps a DICOM Object into a Map. The idea is to have an in-memory model of the DICOM Objects document tree.
